42th openheart https://www.openheart.icu/arithmetic/206.-reverse-linked-list/ -<h1 id="reverse-a-singly-linked-listhttpsleetcode-cncomproblemsreverse-linked-list"><a href="https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/reverse-linked-list">Reverse a singly linked list.</a></h1>
<p>Example:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Input: 1-&gt;2-&gt;3-&gt;4-&gt;5-&gt;NULL
Output: 5-&gt;4-&gt;3-&gt;2-&gt;1-&gt;NULL</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Follow up:</p>
<p>A linked list can be reversed either iteratively or recursively. Could you implement both?</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="迭代">迭代</h2>
<p>将</p>
<blockquote>
<p>1-&gt;2-&gt;3-&gt;4-&gt;5-&gt;NULL</p>
</blockquote>
<p>转化为</p>
<blockquote>
<p>NULL&lt;-1&lt;-2&lt;-3&lt;-4&lt;-5</p>
</blockquote>
<p>使用一个prev节点存储上一个节点（初始为NULL），将当前curr节点的next指向prev节点，prev节点存储curr节点，curr存储curr的原next节点，完成一次迭代。最后返回prev（最后的curr是原ListNode的NULL）</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span style="color:#228b22">/**
</span><span style="color:#228b22"> * Definition for singly-linked list.
</span><span style="color:#228b22"> * public class ListNode {
</span><span style="color:#228b22"> *     int val;
</span><span style="color:#228b22"> *     ListNode next;
</span><span style="color:#228b22"> *     ListNode(int x) { val = x; }
</span><span style="color:#228b22"> * }
</span><span style="color:#228b22"> */</span>
<span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">public</span> ListNode <span style="color:#008b45">reverseList</span>(ListNode head) {
    ListNode prev = <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">null</span>;
    ListNode curr = head;
    <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">while</span> (curr != <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">null</span>) {
        ListNode nextTemp = curr.<span style="color:#658b00">next</span>;
        curr.<span style="color:#658b00">next</span> = prev;
        prev = curr;
        curr = nextTemp;
    }
    <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">return</span> prev;
}
</code></pre></div><h3 id="时间复杂度分析">时间复杂度分析</h3>
<p>时间复杂度：<em>O</em>(n)</p>
<p>空间复杂度：<em>O</em>(1)</p>
<h2 id="递归">递归</h2>
<p>将
$$
n_1→&hellip;→n_{k−1}→n_k→n_{k+1}→&hellip;→n_m→∅
$$
转化为
$$
n_1→&hellip;→n_{k−1}→n_k→n_{k+1}←&hellip;←n_m
$$
先转化原链表最后一个节点，然后依次转化直到n<!-- raw HTML omitted -->1<!-- raw HTML omitted --></p>
<div class="highlight"><pre style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">public</span> ListNode <span style="color:#008b45">reverseList</span>(ListNode head) {
    <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">if</span> (head == <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">null</span> || head.<span style="color:#658b00">next</span> == <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">null</span>) <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">return</span> head;
    ListNode p = reverseList(head.<span style="color:#658b00">next</span>);
    head.<span style="color:#658b00">next</span>.<span style="color:#658b00">next</span> = head;
    head.<span style="color:#658b00">next</span> = <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">null</span>;
    <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">return</span> p;
}
</code></pre></div><h3 id="时间复杂度分析-1">时间复杂度分析</h3>
<p>时间复杂度：O(n)，假设 n 是列表的长度，那么时间复杂度为 O(n)。</p>
<p>空间复杂度：O(n)，由于使用递归，将会使用隐式栈空间。递归深度可能会达到 n 层。</p>
